### 1. 用户注册接口
# 测试场景：注册一个新的普通用户
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "zhangsan",
  "password": "123456"
}

### 2. 注册异常测试 - 用户名重复
# 测试场景：再次运行上面的请求，应该返回 "用户名已被注册" 的错误
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "zhangsan",
  "password": "123456"
}

### 3. 注册异常测试 - 参数缺失
# 测试场景：不传密码，测试后端校验（如果有校验的话）
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "lisi"
}